    <string name="section_tasker">Auto-sync without opening Obsidian</string>
    <string name="tasker_body">Obsidian Sync only refreshes this phone\'s files while the Obsidian app is open. To update the watch automatically — with no PC — use an automation app like Tasker:\n\n1. New Profile → Time (e.g. every 12 hours).\n2. Task → App → Launch App: Obsidian.\n3. Task → Wait: 30 seconds (let Obsidian Sync pull).\n4. Task → Send Intent:\n   • Action: com.example.obsidiantaskspebblebridge.SYNC_NOW\n   • Package: com.bquelhas.obsidiantasks\n   • Target: Broadcast Receiver\n5. (Optional) Task → Go Home.\n\nTip: exclude Tasker and Obsidian from battery optimization, or Android may kill them.</string>
